text: Poolesville High School is a public high school in Poolesville, Maryland. In 2013, Newsweek ranked it as the number one school in the state of Maryland. ==References== ==Other websites== *Poolesville High School *Global Ecology Studies Program *Humanities House *Science, Math, and Computer Science House *Maryland High School Sports and Projected Enrollment *Poolesville High School Athletic Booster Club *Follow Poolesville Athletics on Twitter Category:Buildings and structures in Maryland Category:High schools in the United States
